    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few minor door dings, and the clear coat is starting to thin on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some light staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character and routine maintenance.",
      "price": 19500.0,
