    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for a great opportunity! This vehicle is in budget-friendly, project-ready condition and is looking for a new owner who appreciates a diamond in the rough. While it needs some dedicated mechanical attention and TLC to get back to its best, it's a fantastic choice for anyone looking for an affordable entry into car ownership or a rewarding weekend project!",
