    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, having been kept in a consistent maintenance routine throughout its life. The exterior presents beautifully, showing off a vibrant finish with only minor surface wear consistent with standard highway driving. Inside, you will find a pristine, smoke-free environment where the upholstery remains firm and free of significant wear or staining. Every feature, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, with no leaks or deferred maintenance items. It is a dependable, high-quality car that offers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
